00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:38.820
that to multi-electron atoms,
but making a few of changes

00:04:38.820 --> 00:04:41.420
and making a few modifications
to take into the fact that

00:04:41.420 --> 00:04:43.410
we're going to have
electron-electron repulsions

00:04:43.410 --> 00:04:46.140
going on, we'll be able to think
about any multi-electron

00:04:46.140 --> 00:04:50.280
atom using these same general
ideas, and the Schrodinger

00:04:50.280 --> 00:04:52.910
equation ideas that we came up
with and have looked at for

00:04:52.910 --> 00:04:53.440
the hydrogen atom.

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:56.600
And this is really good news
because it's good to get

00:04:56.600 --> 00:04:57.350
