00:14:15.910 --> 00:14:19.430
So if we're looking at these two
situations here and we're

00:14:19.430 --> 00:14:22.560
actually thinking of them from
a more classical standpoint,

00:14:22.560 --> 00:14:25.220
which is natural for us to do
because we live our lives in

00:14:25.220 --> 00:14:27.740
the every day world, not
thinking about things on the

00:14:27.740 --> 00:14:30.320
atomic size scale all the
time, most of us.

00:14:30.320 --> 00:14:35.070
So, for example, if we were to
look at this 3 s orbital here,

00:14:35.070 --> 00:14:38.710
you might have the question of
how this can be, because we're

00:14:38.710 --> 00:14:42.490
