have probability of having an

00:14:42.490 --> 00:14:45.450
electron here, an electron
can also be way out

00:14:45.450 --> 00:14:46.950
at this radius here.

00:14:46.950 --> 00:14:49.260
But what we're saying is there's
a node here, so that

00:14:49.260 --> 00:14:52.440
there's no probability of
finding an electron between

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:53.820
those two points.

00:14:53.820 --> 00:14:56.440
So you can think of it, if we
were to just think of it as a

00:14:56.440 --> 00:14:59.230
