through point b.

00:15:07.260 --> 00:15:10.540
So, that can be a little bit
confusing for us to think

00:15:10.540 --> 00:15:13.830
about, and when it's a very good
question you might, in

00:15:13.830 --> 00:15:17.610
fact, say well, maybe there's
not zero probability here,

00:15:17.610 --> 00:15:20.600
maybe it's just this teeny,
teeny, tiny number, and in

00:15:20.600 --> 00:15:23.580
